Lanre Gentry, ex-husband of Nigerian actress, Mercy Aigbe, has taken to his Instagram channel to heap praises on his current wife. Gentry’s eulogizing Instagram post is coming just days after calling Mercy Aigbe foul names. Sharing a video collage of his wife cradling their newborn, Lanre wrote: “Is good to have write partner. I will always be grateful to my God.” Read Also: Lanre Gentry shades ex-wife Mercy Aigbe on Instagram Meanwhile, tons of netizens who left comments on the post backed his statement with wishes for his new marriage to be successful. 